wikipedia_page.main: Conor Ramsay (born 9 March 1993) is a Scottish professional footballer who plays for Arthurlie in the Scottish Junior Football Association, West Region. He is a former Scotland youth international and has previously played in the Scottish Premier League for St Mirren.

response: Morton sign two youngsters, Creag Little and Conor Ramsay, from rivals St Mirren on free transfers.
